title: RuiChy 8 Pcs Sponge Ball Cat Toys, Soft Bright Color Foam Soccer Toy Balls, Noise-Free Bouncy Interactive Pet Ball Toys Kitten Activity Chase Quiet Play Chewing Exercise Toy
features: 【Elastic Material】: RuiChy pet ball toys are made with non-toxic high quality sponge material, durable, great for fetch, training, chewing and teething, safe for pets.
【Product Size】: Each ball toy diameter approx 4 cm / 1.6 inch. Small and soft enough for your kitten to bite into like a prey and move around, suitable for small pets.

【Bright Color】: Four different color and eye catching football design makes this ball easy to retrieve in outdoor and it’s also easier to attract your pet's interest. Bright colors stimulate cats to add excitement to playtime. Soft, light and nontoxic sponge balls for kitty safety.

【Super Bouncy】: RuiChy cat balls are lightweight and bouncy, so you can toss them against a wall with no fear of damage. If you drop it on a hard floor, you can hear it and it will bounce. Noise free cat balls won't keep you up all night.

【Interactive Toy】: A good toy to spend you cat's boring time, make interactive fun with your pet. Reduce their damage to sofas, shoes, books, and so on. Package includes 8 pcs pet foam ball toys (2 pcs in each color).
